sections.heading: clause.The Uniform Deployed Parents Custody and Visitation Act does not affect the validity of a temporary court order concerning custodial responsibility during deployment which was entered before January 1, 2016

sections.text:
43-4630.Savings clause.

The Uniform Deployed Parents Custody and Visitation Act does not affect the validity of a temporary court order concerning custodial responsibility during deployment which was entered before January 1, 2016.

SourceLaws 2015, LB219, ยง 30.
